00:00:01.070 --> 00:00:06.410
One specific example for the men's side
platform is the Google Display Network.

00:00:06.410 --> 00:00:10.820
The Google Display Network GDN is
a collection of over a million websites,

00:00:10.820 --> 00:00:14.350
apps, videos, and
blogs that show AdWords ads.

00:00:14.350 --> 00:00:18.170
Basically these million plus sites are
using Google to help them offer their

00:00:18.170 --> 00:00:21.160
page to monetize by
providing advertisers with

00:00:21.160 --> 00:00:23.410
online real estate to advertise on.

00:00:23.410 --> 00:00:27.190
The Google algorithm will target
the ads to the appropriate audience

00:00:27.190 --> 00:00:30.060
by ensuring that the ads
are relevant for the page content.

00:00:31.620 --> 00:00:35.740
Will do this matching based on the
keywords you select and other factors.

00:00:35.740 --> 00:00:39.400
This will give you a much wider audience
than just being in search results.

00:00:40.460 --> 00:00:41.130
&gt;&gt; With GDN,

00:00:41.130 --> 00:00:44.400
you have the opportunity to fine tune
where you want your ads to be seen.

00:00:44.400 --> 00:00:47.290
Beyond selecting audience
based on key words,

00:00:47.290 --> 00:00:49.770
you can choose topics to
narrow your audience.

00:00:49.770 --> 00:00:54.150
So for Abarkment we can choose to
focus on dog related websites or

00:00:54.150 --> 00:00:57.110
pick a specific site like
one that sells pet supplies.

00:00:57.110 --> 00:01:00.530
Or we can block our ads from certain
sites that aren't relevant to what we

00:01:00.530 --> 00:01:04.970
do, like a site that's dedicated
to hating dogs and loving cats.

00:01:04.970 --> 00:01:08.452
We can even focus on people who
have been to our site before and

00:01:08.452 --> 00:01:10.690
re target them when
they go to other sites.

00:01:10.690 --> 00:01:12.280
This is called remarketing and

00:01:12.280 --> 00:01:14.320
you can find out more about
that in the instructor notes.

00:01:15.590 --> 00:01:17.210
&gt;&gt; It's called a display network.

00:01:17.210 --> 00:01:20.650
Because unlike Google search,
where you can use only text ads.

00:01:20.650 --> 00:01:24.330
Here you can display all types
of formats like text, image,

00:01:24.330 --> 00:01:26.410
interactive, and video ads.

00:01:26.410 --> 00:01:28.600
To learn more about this check
out the instructor notes.

