different sites on their mobile phone.

00:01:52.680 --> 00:01:56.450
And they may see one of your ads and
decide to click on it and

00:01:56.450 --> 00:01:57.610
go to your mobile site.

00:01:57.610 --> 00:02:02.180
So that's our regular mobile GDN,
Google Display Network,

00:02:02.180 --> 00:02:05.150
